\\hline
Type & Core ($\\mu$m) & Cladding ($\\mu$m) & Mode \\\\
\\hline
50/125 & 50.0 & 125 & Multimode, graded index \\\\
62.5/125 & 62.5 & 125 & Multimode, graded index \\\\
100/125 & 100.0 & 125 & Multimode, graded index \\\\
