\\textbf{Note:} All calculations are in modulo $2^{32}$.

\\begin{itemize}
    \\item \\textbf{Time-out occurred.} Resend the first segment in the queue. Reset the timer.
    \\item \\textbf{A corrupted ACK arrived.} Discard it.
    \\item \\textbf{A duplicate ACK arrived that acknowledges the segment in front of the queue.} Slide the window ($S_f = \\text{ackNo}$) and adjust the window size. Remove the segment from the queue. If any segment is left in the queue, restart the timer.
    \\item \\textbf{A duplicate ACK arrived.} Set $\\text{dupNo} = \\text{dupNo} + 1$. If ($\\text{dupNo} = 3$) resend the segment in front of the queue, restart the timer, and set $\\text{dupNo} = 0$.
\\end{itemize}

